This is a sample Android widget that displays the battery level  

Based on an idea from Redditor lyricalsnyper

http://www.reddit.com/r/Android/comments/hj9oe/does_anyone_know_of_a_battery_widget_that_looks/

Getting Started
===============

1. Long Click on your desktop to bring up widget menu
2. Select Battery Widget
3. Profit..

